        <h3 class="font-semibold text-neutral-900 mb-2">Software Developer from India, $120,000 salary</h3>
        <p class="text-neutral-600 mb-4">Sydney tech company, 5 years experience, medium-term stream.</p>
        <p class="text-green-700 font-medium">✓ Well above salary threshold. ACS skills assessment took 8 weeks. Got Bupa OVHC ($180/month). Visa processed in 3 months. Now on PR pathway—will apply for ENS 186 after 3 years. Company covered all visa costs.</p>
