        <p class="text-amber-700 font-medium">△ Just above TSMIT. Has Medicare access via RHCA but still needed private insurance for visa. Got NIB OVHC basic ($150/month). Short-term stream—no PR pathway, but visa renewable once. Uses Medicare for bulk-billed GP visits, private for extras.</p>
